35#include "gsskrb5_locl.h"
36
37OM_uint32 GSSAPI_CALLCONV
38_gsskrb5_localname(OM_uint32 *minor_status,
39 gss_const_name_t pname,
40 const gss_OID mech_type,
41 gss_buffer_t localname)
42{
43 krb5_error_code ret;
44 krb5_context context;
45 krb5_const_principal princ = (krb5_const_principal)pname;
46 char lnamebuf[256];
47
48 GSSAPI_KRB5_INIT(&context);
49
50 *minor_status = 0;
51
52 ret = krb5_aname_to_localname(context, princ,
53 sizeof(lnamebuf), lnamebuf);
54 if (ret != 0) {
55 *minor_status = ret;
56 return GSS_S_FAILURE;
57 }
58
59 localname->length = strlen(lnamebuf);
60
61 localname->value = malloc(localname->length + 1);
62 if (localname->value == NULL) {
63 localname->length = 0;
64 *minor_status = ENOMEM;
65 return GSS_S_FAILURE;
66 }
67
68 memcpy(localname->value, lnamebuf, localname->length + 1);
69 *minor_status = 0;
70
71 return GSS_S_COMPLETE;
72}
